### Project 2.1: Customer Revenue & Retention Analysis
This project analyzes customer spending and retention using SQL.  
It demonstrates joins, subqueries, aggregations, and window functions.

**Highlights:**
- Top 5 customers by lifetime value  
- Revenue by region and month  
- Detection of inactive customers (churn simulation)  
- Product category revenue share  
- Customer ranking by total spend  

**Tools:** MySQL / SQLite  
**Skills:** Joins 路 GROUP BY 路 Window Functions 路 Date Functions 路 Business Logic
Uses the customer_revenue_analysis.sql
